== A92170000 – Player's Handbook (2014)== The ''[[Player's Handbook]]'' is one of the core rulebooks for the Dungeons & Dragons [[Editions of Dungeons & Dragons#Dungeons & Dragons 5th edition|5th edition]], published in 2014. An assortment of monsters, associated with [[Character class (Dungeons & Dragons)|class]] traits and spells, are described in Appendix D.
