 (2000), Monster Manual (2003), Monster Manual (2008), Monster Vault (2010) |Variants=Yuan-ti Malison, Yuan-ti Pureblood |Description= }} |}
==A92180000 – Monster Manual (2014)== The ''[[Monster Manual]]'' is one of the core rulebooks for the Dungeons & Dragons [[Editions of Dungeons & Dragons#Dungeons & Dragons 5th edition|5th edition]], published in 2014. The book features an introduction on pages 4–11, the monster descriptions on pages 12–316, an appendix of Miscellaneous Creatures on pages 317–341, and a second appendix of Nonplayer Characters on pages 342–350.
A list of the monsters by Challenge Rating was not included in the book, and was instead posted on Wizards of the Coast's web site.<ref name=InfoFromWotC4a>{{cite web| url=http://media.wizards.com/2014/downloads/dnd/MM_MonstersCR.pdf|title=Monsters by Challenge Rating|accessdate=2014-09-22}}</ref> The list was also provided in the 5th edition ''Dungeon Master's Guide''.
{{ISBN|978-0-7869-6561-8}}
