==A96070000 – The Rise of Tiamat (2014)== ''[[The Rise of Tiamat]]'' is the second adventure module for the 5th edition ''[[Dungeons & Dragons]]'' line, following ''Hoard of the Dragon Queen''.<ref name="forbes">https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidewalt/2014/05/30/new-dungeons-dragons-release-dates-details/</ref> It contains statistics for some of the monsters described in the module in Appendix A; the rest are in an online supplement.<ref name=InfoFromWotC4>{{cite web| url=http://dnd.wizards.com/products/tabletop-games/rpg-products/rise-tiamat|title=The Rise of Tiamat|accessdate=2017-02-10}}</ref>
{{ISBN|978-0-7869-6565-6}}
