==B24360000 – Princes of the Apocalypse (2015)== ''Princes of the Apocalypse'' is the third adventure module for the 5th edition ''[[Dungeons & Dragons]]'' line.<ref name="arstechnica">https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2016/02/reviewed-dungeons-dragons-5th-edition/</ref> It contains statistics for some of the monsters described in the module in Chapter 7; the rest are in an online supplement.<ref name=InfoFromWotC5>{{cite web| url=http://dnd.wizards.com/products/tabletop-games/rpg-products/princes-apocalypse|title=Princes of the Apocalypse|accessdate=2017-02-10}}</ref>
