==B86690000 – Storm King's Thunder (2016)== ''Storm King's Thunder'' is the sixth adventure module for the 5th edition ''[[Dungeons & Dragons]]'' line.<ref name="isolaillyon">http://www.isolaillyon.it/2016/06/04/dd-ecco-storm-kings-thunder-e-volos-guide-to-monsters.html</ref> It contains statistics for the new monsters described in the module in Appendix C.
{{ISBN|978-0-7869-6600-4}}
