==C22070000 – Tales from the Yawning Portal (2017)== ''Tales from the Yawning Portal'' is the seventh adventure module for the 5th edition ''[[Dungeons & Dragons]]'' line.<ref name="purplepawn2017">http://www.purplepawn.com/2017/04/second-look-tales-from-the-yawning-portal</ref> It contains statistics for the new monsters described in the module in Appendix B.
{{ISBN|978-0-7869-6609-7}}
