==C22080000 – Tomb of Annihilation (2017)== ''Tomb of Annihilation'' is the eighth adventure module for the 5th edition ''[[Dungeons & Dragons]]'' line.<ref name="purplepawn2017a">http://www.purplepawn.com/2017/06/dds-tomb-of-annihilation</ref> It contains statistics for the new monsters described in the module in Appendix D.
{{ISBN|978-0-7869-6610-3}}
