==C45940000 – Mordenkainen's Tome of Foes (2018)== ''Mordenkainen's Tome of Foes'' introduces over 100 monsters to the 5th edition ''[[Dungeons & Dragons]]'' line.<ref name="ComicBookCom1">http://comicbook.com/gaming/2018/05/23/dungeons-and-dragons-mordenkainens-tome-of-foes-review/</ref> The book features a preface on page 4, a chapter on the [[Fiend (Dungeons & Dragons)#Blood_War|Blood War]] on pages 5–34, a chapter on Elves on pages 35–63, a chapter on Dwarves and Duergar on pages 65–83, a chapter on Gith on pages 85–97, a chapter on Halflings and Gnomes on pages 99–114, new monster descriptions on pages 115–252, and an appendix of Monster Lists on pages 253–256. One contribution to the book, the Oblex, was created by [[Make-A-Wish Foundation]] recipient Nolan Whale.<ref name="MakeAWish">http://comicbook.com/gaming/2018/05/23/dungeons-and-dragons-make-a-wish-mordenkainens-tome-of-foes/</ref>
